Project: IrssiBot
2010 GPL

== Quickstart ==

Download IrssiBot:
 $ cd ~/.irssi
 $ git clone git://github.com/koenbollen/irssibot

Install:
 $ mkdir -p scripts
 $ ln -s ../irssibot/irssibot.pl scripts/
 $ echo "/run irssibot" >> startup

Enable plugins:
 $ cd irssibot/plugins/autoload
 $ ln -s ../date.py


